♪ I remember Big Joe Turner ♪

46:27.833 --> 46:30.916
♪ What he sounds like when he sings ♪

46:33.750 --> 46:38.208
♪ I remember you ♪

46:38.791 --> 46:41.333
♪ But I can't remember love ♪

46:41.416 --> 46:42.250
[door closes]

46:45.708 --> 46:47.708
[bottles clanking]

46:56.083 --> 46:58.000
[phone rings]

47:01.125 --> 47:01.958
[phone rings]

47:03.458 --> 47:04.291
Hello.

47:05.083 --> 47:05.916
[Beltik] Beth?

47:07.166 --> 47:08.000
Hello?

47:11.708 --> 47:13.583
["Venus" by Shocking Blue playing]

