♪ A goddess on a mountain top ♪

47:34.250 --> 47:36.875
♪ Was burning like a silver flame ♪

47:38.000 --> 47:40.666
-[volume increases]
-♪ The summit of beauty and love ♪

47:42.083 --> 47:43.625
♪ And Venus was her name ♪

47:45.208 --> 47:46.083
♪ She's got it ♪

47:48.041 --> 47:50.041
♪ Yeah, baby, she's got it ♪

