♪ Well, I'm your Venus ♪

48:02.833 --> 48:05.666
♪ I'm your fire
At your desire ♪

48:14.958 --> 48:15.875
[vomits]

48:22.750 --> 48:25.500
♪ Her weapons were her crystal eyes ♪

48:26.666 --> 48:28.833
♪ Making every man mad ♪

48:30.375 --> 48:33.625
♪ Black as the dark night she was ♪

48:33.708 --> 48:35.708
♪ Got what no one else had ♪

48:36.458 --> 48:37.333
♪ Wow! ♪

48:37.416 --> 48:38.666
♪ She's got it ♪

48:38.750 --> 48:40.083
