49:26.000 --> 49:28.041
♪ Well, I'm your Venus ♪

49:28.708 --> 49:31.541
♪ I'm your fire
At your desire ♪

49:38.541 --> 49:40.083
-[song stops abruptly]
-[bottles clatter]

49:40.166 --> 49:41.291
That's my girl.

49:44.291 --> 49:45.291
[car door slams]

49:51.625 --> 49:52.458
[car door slams]

50:01.916 --> 50:04.750
[loud knocking]

50:06.583 --> 50:07.416
Beth?

50:10.708 --> 50:11.583
Are you in there?

50:14.250 --> 50:15.541
I've been calling.

50:16.625 --> 50:17.875
[distantly] Are you okay?

50:18.875 --> 50:20.000
I'm worried about you.

50:23.500 --> 50:24.583
Beth, it's Harry.

50:26.375 --> 50:28.333
[loud knocking]

50:28.833 --> 50:31.166
Beth, if you're in there,
please open the door.

50:47.500 --> 50:49.666
[phone rings]

50:52.333 --> 50:54.583
[phone rings]

50:57.416 --> 50:59.416
[phone rings]

51:01.041 --> 51:02.208
[phone rings]

51:03.041 --> 51:03.875
Hello.

51:04.416 --> 51:05.583
[man] Elizabeth Harmon?

51:06.500 --> 51:08.791
-Yeah.
-This is Ed Spencer.

51:12.041 --> 51:12.875
Okay.

51:13.458 --> 51:15.291
I'm the local tournament director.

51:15.375 --> 51:16.750
I'm calling about tomorrow.

51:18.291 --> 51:19.125
Tomorrow?

51:19.666 --> 51:20.500
The tournament.

51:21.208 --> 51:23.375
We were wondering
if you could come an hour early.

51:23.458 --> 51:25.583
The Louisville paper
is sending a photographer,

51:25.666 --> 51:27.791
and we think WLEX will have somebody.

51:28.791 --> 51:29.958
Could you come at nine?

51:32.833 --> 51:33.916
Miss Harmon?

51:34.000 --> 51:35.791
Uh, yeah, um…

51:36.750 --> 51:38.333
I'll be there at 9:30.

51:40.000 --> 51:42.666
Half an hour is more than enough time
to take the pictures.

51:44.958 --> 51:45.791
Shit.

51:47.791 --> 51:48.625
Fuck.

51:49.916 --> 51:50.833
[sighs]

52:00.833 --> 52:01.791
Oh, shit.

52:02.458 --> 52:03.375
[man] Beth.

52:04.166 --> 52:05.041
Ed Spencer.

52:06.041 --> 52:08.291
-You made it.
-Yeah, hi. Um…

52:09.708 --> 52:12.125
You wouldn't happen to have any aspirin?

52:12.208 --> 52:14.500
-I'm sure I could find you some.
-Thank you.

52:16.083 --> 52:18.000
-N-no.
-[woman] Beth Harmon?

52:20.000 --> 52:21.041
Annette Packer.

52:21.791 --> 52:24.500
I was your first official win.
You cleaned my clock.

52:24.583 --> 52:27.250
-The whole thing lasted about 15 minutes.
-Sorry.

52:27.333 --> 52:28.875
Oh, don't be, it's an honor.

52:28.958 --> 52:30.250
I'm always telling people

52:30.333 --> 52:33.541
that I was there for
two of your big firsts.

52:35.833 --> 52:39.333
I… I knew you were going places,
and that meant something to me.

52:40.166 --> 52:41.000
You know?

52:41.083 --> 52:42.916
That it was possible…

52:44.166 --> 52:45.000
for us.

52:48.000 --> 52:50.458
So, are you playing here today?

52:50.541 --> 52:52.000
[chuckles] Oh, God, no.

52:52.083 --> 52:54.125
I haven't played in a few years now.

52:54.208 --> 52:56.625
I'm premed, so I have exactly zero time.

52:56.708 --> 52:57.541
[chuckles]

52:58.833 --> 53:00.833
I, um, I-I do miss it, though.

53:02.708 --> 53:03.541
Yeah.

53:04.458 --> 53:08.166
I, uh, I heard you were gonna be here,
so I came down for the weekend.

53:09.208 --> 53:10.708
To thank you in person.

53:16.333 --> 53:17.166
Anyway,

53:17.916 --> 53:18.916
I'll see you inside.

53:21.375 --> 53:22.208
Bye.

53:31.083 --> 53:32.000
[whispering] Shit.

53:34.500 --> 53:36.333
[in normal voice] Oh, thank you.

53:36.416 --> 53:38.166
There's no smoking in here.

53:39.541 --> 53:41.041
Right, of course. Thanks.

53:43.541 --> 53:45.416
[Ed] Play starts in a few minutes.

53:45.500 --> 53:46.333
[Beth] Right on!

53:48.916 --> 53:49.875
[lighter clicking]

53:51.833 --> 53:52.708
Goddamnit!

53:57.250 --> 53:58.083
[car door slams]

54:06.625 --> 54:07.875
You got a new car.

54:09.750 --> 54:11.875
Yeah, I, uh, I wrecked the other one.

54:13.291 --> 54:14.291
This one's more me.

54:15.666 --> 54:16.875
Are you here to play or…

54:17.416 --> 54:19.875
-No.
-Well, what are you doing here?

54:22.291 --> 54:23.416
I've been calling.

54:24.916 --> 54:26.166
I even came by one time.

54:27.958 --> 54:29.083
Did you?

54:29.166 --> 54:30.000
Yeah.

54:32.000 --> 54:33.166
I'm worried about you.

54:35.250 --> 54:36.625
What on earth for? [chuckles]

54:37.125 --> 54:39.458
I've seen you once or twice
at the supermarket.

54:40.291 --> 54:41.208
You following me?

54:41.291 --> 54:42.250
I work there.

54:44.041 --> 54:45.166
What?

54:45.583 --> 54:48.416
I'm Assistant Manager,
so I'm usually in the office.

54:51.208 --> 54:52.333
You've never said hello.

54:52.833 --> 54:54.041
Well, you didn't seem…

54:55.333 --> 54:56.458
approachable.

55:00.583 --> 55:01.500
You need help.

55:01.583 --> 55:03.375
What kind of help would that be?

55:04.333 --> 55:05.916
Help with my chess? We tried that--

55:06.000 --> 55:09.125
-That's not what I'm talking about.
-What are we talking about?

55:11.291 --> 55:12.458
My dad drank.

55:13.958 --> 55:15.750
He wasn't mean or anything.

55:15.833 --> 55:18.250
He just got quiet
and fell asleep in his clothes.

55:21.083 --> 55:23.250
-Okay.
-You smell just like he did.

55:24.291 --> 55:25.958
Your eyes are just like his eyes,

55:26.875 --> 55:28.625
-and your skin is--
-My skin?

55:28.708 --> 55:29.791
Like I said…

55:31.125 --> 55:32.083
I'm worried about you.

55:32.166 --> 55:34.041
Sounds more like
you're feeling sorry for me.

55:34.125 --> 55:35.333
I didn't say that.

55:35.416 --> 55:38.166
I'm not the one supposed to be in college,
not working in a supermarket.

55:38.250 --> 55:39.125
I'm doing both.

55:39.208 --> 55:40.208
You know what?

55:41.458 --> 55:42.833
Yeah, I like working there.

55:43.833 --> 55:45.916
It's a good job, and the people are nice.

55:47.083 --> 55:48.000
[Ed] Elizabeth!

55:51.625 --> 55:52.500
[car door opens]

55:53.375 --> 55:54.333
Good luck, Beth.

55:57.625 --> 56:00.166
-[car door closes]
-[engine turns over]

56:02.250 --> 56:04.250
[car drives away]

56:05.833 --> 56:07.208
[melancholy music playing]

56:09.250 --> 56:11.250
[panting]

56:30.041 --> 56:30.916
[engine stops]

56:37.916 --> 56:39.375
[rapping on door]

56:42.833 --> 56:44.041
[rapping continues]

56:47.458 --> 56:49.208
-[rapping continues]
-[Beth thuds]

56:49.291 --> 56:51.416
[Beth] Ow! Damn it! Harry!

56:53.333 --> 56:55.750
I told you to leave me alone!

56:58.625 --> 57:01.291
Jesus fucking Christ.

57:03.125 --> 57:05.833
Who the hell are you?

57:07.666 --> 57:08.500
Jolene?

57:13.291 --> 57:15.625
[theme music playing]
